#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "BookMan: Organize your Bookmarks"
msgstr "BookMan: स्वस्य Bookmarks व्यवस्थितं कुर्वन्तु"

#. Tag: primary
#: bookmarks.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks"
msgstr "बुकमार्क्स"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"BookMan is &krusader;'s Bookmark tool for bookmarking folders, local and "
"<link linkend=\"remote-connections\">remote &URL;s</link>, and later "
"returning to them in a click of a button. The Bookman menu is divided into "
"four sections:"
msgstr ""
"BookMan &amp;krusader;&#39;s Bookmark tool अस्ति यत् समुच्चय, स्थानीय तथा...<link "
"linkend=\"remote-connections\"> दूरस्थ &amp;URL;s</link> , पश्चात् च बटनस्य क्लिक् "
"करणेन तेषु प्रत्यागत्य । Bookman मेनू चतुर्षु विभागेषु विभक्तम् अस्ति :"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid "Your personal bookmarks"
msgstr "भवतः व्यक्तिगतपुस्तकचिह्नानि"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Popular &URL;s</para>"
msgstr "<para>लोकप्रिय &URL;s</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Permanent bookmarks</para>"
msgstr "<para>स्थायिपुस्तकचिह्नानि</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Manage bookmarks</para>"
msgstr "<para>पुस्तकचिह्नानि प्रबन्धयन्तु</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can bookmark inside a remote file system (&FTP; or SAMBA) and later use "
"the bookmark to quickly connect to the remote machine, but you cannot "
"bookmark inside an archive."
msgstr ""
"भवान् दूरस्थसञ्चिकातन्त्रस्य (&FTP; अथवा SAMBA) अन्तः बुकमार्कं कर्तुं शक्नोति पश्चात् "
"दूरस्थयन्त्रेण सह शीघ्रं सम्बद्धं कर्तुं बुकमार्कस्य उपयोगं कर्तुं शक्नोति, परन्तु संग्रहालयस्य अन्तः "
"बुकमार्कं कर्तुं न शक्नोति"

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Bookmark menu</title>"
msgstr "<title>बुकमार्क मेनू</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: bookmarks.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Bookmark menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>पुस्तकचिह्नमेनू</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Bookmarks"
msgstr "बुकमार्कस्य उपयोगः"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Usually, you click on the <guibutton>BookMan II</guibutton> button (the "
"rightmost button to the right of the address bar at the top of the active "
"panel) when you are in the target folder. For example, to bookmark <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr/tmp</filename>, navigate &krusader; there and click "
"the <guibutton>BookMan II</guibutton> button and select "
"<guimenuitem>Bookmark Current</guimenuitem>. When the <guilabel>Add "
"Bookmark</guilabel> dialog box appears, the &URL; line will say <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/usr/tmp</filename>. <guilabel>Name</guilabel> is for "
"the name you would like to give to the bookmark (&eg;: temporary folder). "
"Hotkeys are supported by adding <literal>&amp;</literal> to the bookmark "
"name &eg; <literal>&amp;sourceforge, &amp;home, down&amp;loads</literal> "
"&etc;, so you can quickly call the bookmark name with <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>foo</keycap></keycombo>. If you add the bookmark "
"without entering a name, the bookmarks name will be the same as its target. "
"<guilabel>&URL;</guilabel> is where the bookmark points to. <guilabel>Create "
"in</guilabel> creates bookmark folders for organizing your bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"सामान्यतया, लक्ष्यपुटे स्थित्वा <guibutton>BookMan II</guibutton> बटन् (सक्रियपटलस्य "
"उपरि स्थितस्य पतापट्टिकायाः दक्षिणतः दक्षिणतमं बटनं) नुदति यथा, <filename class="
"\"directory\">/usr/tmp</filename> इति बुकमार्कं कर्तुं &krusader; तत्र "
"<guibutton>BookMan II</guibutton> बटन् नुत्वा <guimenuitem>Bookmark Current</"
"guimenuitem> इति चिनोतु । यदा <guilabel>Add Bookmark</guilabel> संवादपेटिका "
"दृश्यते तदा &URL; रेखा <filename class=\"directory\">/usr/tmp</filename> इति "
"वदिष्यति । <guilabel>नाम</guilabel> इति नाम यत् भवन्तः पुस्तकचिह्नं दातुम् इच्छन्ति "
"(&eg;: अस्थायी पुटम्) । हॉटकीजः बुकमार्कनाम्नि <literal>&amp;</literal> योजयित्वा "
"समर्थिताः भवन्ति &eg; <literal>&amp;sourceforge, &amp;home, down&amp;loads</"
"literal> &etc;, अतः भवान् <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>foo</"
"keycap></keycombo> इति । यदि भवान् नाम न प्रविष्ट्वा पुस्तकचिह्नं योजयति तर्हि "
"पुस्तकचिह्ननाम तस्य लक्ष्यस्य समानं भविष्यति । <guilabel>&URL;</guilabel> इति यत्र "
"पुस्तकचिह्नं सूचयति । <guilabel>Create in</guilabel> भवतः पुस्तकचिह्नानां व्यवस्थित्यर्थं "
"पुस्तकचिह्नपुटं निर्माति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use your bookmarks, click the <guibutton>BookMan II</guibutton> button "
"and choose a bookmark. You may also use the <link linkend=\"key_bindings"
"\">Key-Bindings</link>: <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>B</"
"keycap></keycombo> to bookmark the current item, <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt; <keycap>right/left arrow</keycap></keycombo> to open right/left "
"panel bookmarks list and <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>D</"
"keycap></keycombo> to open the bookmarks of the active panel. From the "
"context menu of the bookmark (&RMB; click) you can open it in a new <link "
"linkend=\"folder-tabs\">Folder tab</link>."
msgstr ""
"भवतः पुस्तकचिह्नानां उपयोगाय, क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु<guibutton> पुस्तकपुरुष II</guibutton> बटनं "
"कृत्वा पुस्तकचिह्नं चिनोतु । भवन्तः अपि उपयोक्तुं शक्नुवन्ति<link linkend=\"key_bindings"
"\"> कील-बन्धन</link> : १.<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &amp;Ctrl;<keycap> ख</"
"keycap></keycombo> वर्तमानवस्तुं बुकमार्कं कर्तुं, .<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &amp;"
"अल्ट्;<keycap> दक्षिण/वाम बाण</keycap></keycombo> दक्षिण/वामफलकस्य पुस्तकचिह्नसूचीं "
"उद्घाटयितुं तथा च<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &amp;Ctrl;<keycap> घ</keycap></"
"keycombo> सक्रियपटलस्य पुस्तकचिह्नानि उद्घाटयितुं । पुस्तकचिह्नस्य सन्दर्भमेनूतः (&amp;RMB; "
"क्लिक्) भवान् नूतनरूपेण उद्घाटयितुं शक्नोति<link linkend=\"folder-tabs\"> समुच्चय ट्याब्</"
"link> ."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is a quick search bar at the top of the <guibutton>BookMan II</"
"guibutton> menu."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>BookMan II</guibutton> मेन्यू इत्यस्य उपरि द्रुत-अन्वेषण-पट्टिका अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The search bar will always be visible in the bookmarks menu if you check the "
"corresponding item on the <link linkend=\"konfig-panel-general\">Panel "
"Konfigurator's page</link>."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् तत्सम्बद्धं द्रव्यं<link linkend=\"konfig-panel-general\"> Panel "
"Configurator इत्यस्य पृष्ठम्</link> ."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Below are the rules to handle bookmarks:"
msgstr "पुस्तकचिह्नानां नियन्त्रणार्थं नियमाः अधः सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Just type letters to search: bookmarks are matched by name prefix"
msgstr "केवलं अन्वेषणार्थं अक्षराणि टङ्कयन्तु: पुस्तकचिह्नानि नाम उपसर्गेण मेलयन्ति"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If multiple bookmarks are matched by the prefix, they are highlighted and "
"the first one is selected - hit &Enter; to activate the bookmark"
msgstr ""
"यदि उपसर्गेण बहुविधाः पुस्तकचिह्नाः मेलिताः भवन्ति तर्हि ते प्रकाशिताः भवन्ति प्रथमः च "
"चयनितः भवति - &Enter; पुस्तकचिह्नं सक्रियं कर्तुं"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once a single bookmark is matched, it is immediately triggered. That is when "
"you type <literal>'h'</literal> and only one bookmark starts with "
"<literal>'h'</literal>, it is executed immediately - no &Enter; needed"
msgstr ""
"एकदा एकं पुस्तकचिह्नं मेलितं जातं चेत् तत् तत्क्षणमेव प्रवर्तते । तत् यदा भवान् <literal>'h'</"
"literal> इति टङ्कयति तथा च केवलं एकः पुस्तकचिह्नः <literal>'h'</literal> इत्यनेन "
"आरभ्यते तदा तत्क्षणमेव निष्पादितं भवति - न &Enter; आवश्यकम्"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accelerators work only if the keystroke is the first one"
msgstr "त्वरकाः तदा एव कार्यं कुर्वन्ति यदा कीलप्रहारः प्रथमः भवति"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Backspace; is supported"
msgstr "&पृष्ठस्थान; समर्थितम् अस्ति"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search is case insensitive unless you type a capital letter. That is typing "
"<literal>HamBurglar</literal> will only match <literal>HamBurglar</literal> "
"but not <literal>hamburglar</literal> or <literal>Hamburglar</literal>."
msgstr ""
"यावत् भवन्तः बृहत् अक्षरं न टङ्कयन्ति तावत् अन्वेषणं केस-असंवेदनशीलं भवति । तत् "
"<literal>HamBurglar</literal> इति टङ्कनं केवलं <literal>HamBurglar</literal> "
"इत्यनेन सह मेलनं करिष्यति परन्तु <literal>hamburglar</literal> अथवा "
"<literal>Hamburglar</literal> इति न मेलति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search bar is intentionally a read-only field"
msgstr "अन्वेषणपट्टिका इच्छया केवलं पठनीयक्षेत्रम् अस्ति"

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "Password handling"
msgstr "गुप्तशब्दनियन्त्रणम्"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One of the benefits of the <link linkend=\"bookman\">bookmark manager</link> "
"is that the passwords are saved using &plasma;'s services - where &eg; your "
"&konqueror;/&kmail; password are saved. If you have a wallet, &plasma; will "
"save the passwords there. By clicking the bookmarks, a dialog will open and "
"ask for your username and password. Supply them and click <guibutton>Save "
"password</guibutton>. The passwords and usernames will be saved securely by "
"&plasma;'s wallet (make sure it is enabled by your distro). The downside "
"here is that if the system was reinstalled and you do not backup your "
"passwords from the wallet as well as &krusader;'s bookmark file, something "
"will be lost."
msgstr ""
"एकस्य लाभस्य...<link linkend=\"bookman\"> बुकमार्क प्रबन्धक</link> अस्ति यत् "
"गुप्तशब्दाः &amp;plasma; इत्यस्य सेवानां उपयोगेन रक्षिताः भवन्ति - यत्र ⪚ भवतः &amp;"
"konqueror;/&amp;kmail; गुप्तशब्दः रक्षितः भवति। यदि भवतः बटुकं अस्ति तर्हि &amp;"
"plasma; तत्र गुप्तशब्दान् रक्षति। पुस्तकचिह्नानि क्लिक् कृत्वा एकः संवादः उद्घाटितः "
"भविष्यति, भवतः उपयोक्तृनाम गुप्तशब्दं च पृच्छति । तान् आपूर्तिं कृत्वा क्लिक् "
"कुर्वन्तु<guibutton> गुप्तशब्दं रक्षतु</guibutton> . गुप्तशब्दाः उपयोक्तृनामानि च &amp;"
"plasma;-इत्यस्य बटुकेन सुरक्षितरूपेण रक्षिताः भविष्यन्ति (भवतः distro द्वारा सक्षमम् इति "
"सुनिश्चितं कुर्वन्तु) । अत्र दुष्परिणामः अस्ति यत् यदि प्रणाली पुनः संस्थापिता आसीत् तथा च "
"भवान् बटुकात् अपि च &amp;krusader; इत्यस्य बुकमार्कसञ्चिकातः स्वगुप्तशब्दानां बैकअपं न "
"करोति तर्हि किमपि नष्टं भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Popular &URL;s</title>"
msgstr "<title>लोकप्रिय &amp;URL;s</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: bookmarks.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Popular &URL;s</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>लोकप्रिय &URL;s</primary>"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The submenu <guilabel>Popular &URL;s</guilabel> holds persistent the most "
"popular visited &URL;s (local or remote). This submenu displays the top 15 "
"popular &URL;s, sorted by ranking, so that the top &URL; is the most "
"popular. This is easy for when you need to visit &URL;s often, but do not "
"want to create <link linkend=\"bookman\">Bookmarks</link>, it serves as a "
"temporary bookmark list for the most visited links. Quicksearch in "
"<guilabel>Popular &URL;s</guilabel> is a fast way to browse/select the "
"popular &URL;s:"
msgstr ""
"उपमेनू<guilabel> लोकप्रिय &amp;URL;s</guilabel> सर्वाधिकं लोकप्रियं भ्रमणं कृतं &amp;"
"URL;s (स्थानीयं वा दूरस्थं वा) निरन्तरं धारयति । एतत् उपमेनू शीर्ष १५ लोकप्रियं &amp;URL;"
"s प्रदर्शयति, श्रेणीद्वारा क्रमबद्धं, येन शीर्षस्थं &amp;URL; इति सर्वाधिकं लोकप्रियम् अस्ति। "
"यदा भवद्भिः &amp;URL;s बहुधा गन्तव्यं भवति, परन्तु सृजितुं न इच्छति तदा एतत् सुलभम्<link "
"linkend=\"bookman\"> बुकमार्क्स</link> , सर्वाधिकं भ्रमणं कृतानां लिङ्कानां कृते अस्थायी "
"बुकमार्कसूचीरूपेण कार्यं करोति । त्वरित अन्वेषण in<guilabel> लोकप्रिय &amp;URL;s</"
"guilabel> लोकप्रिय &amp;URL;s ब्राउज्/चयनस्य द्रुतमार्गः अस्ति:"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the <guilabel>Popular &URL;s</guilabel> or use <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo>"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>लोकप्रिय &URL;s</guilabel> उद्घाटयन्तु अथवा <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type a few letters to narrow the search"
msgstr "अन्वेषणं संकुचितं कर्तुं कतिपयानि अक्षराणि टङ्कयन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press &Enter; (you will go to the &URL; from list)"
msgstr "&Enter इति नुदन्तु; (भवन्तः सूचीतः &URL; इति गमिष्यन्ति)"

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Permanent bookmarks</title>"
msgstr "<title>स्थायी बुकमार्क</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These are hardcoded bookmarks to the top bookmark menu; there is no need for "
"them to be saved to the file. With the <link linkend=\"context-menu"
"\">Context Menu</link> you can enable/disable these permanent bookmarks. The "
"following permanent bookmarks are available:"
msgstr ""
"एते शीर्षपुस्तकचिह्नमेनू प्रति हार्डकोडेड् बुकमार्क्स् सन्ति; तेषां सञ्चिकायां रक्षणस्य आवश्यकता "
"नास्ति । सह<link linkend=\"context-menu\"> सन्दर्भ मेनू</link> एतानि "
"स्थायीपुस्तकचिह्नानि सक्षम/अक्षमं कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति । निम्नलिखितस्थायिपुस्तकचिह्नानि उपलभ्यन्ते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Trash bin</guilabel> uses &plasma;'s <filename>trash:/</filename> "
"protocol."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>कचराबन्दः</guilabel> &plasma;इत्यस्य <filename>trash:/</filename> "
"प्रोटोकॉलस्य उपयोगं करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Local Network</guilabel> uses &plasma;'s <filename>remote:/</"
"filename> protocol."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>स्थानीयसंजाल</guilabel> &plasma;इत्यस्य <filename>remote:/</filename> "
"प्रोटोकॉलस्य उपयोगं करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Virtual Filesystem</guilabel> <link linkend=\"vfs\">Virtual file "
"systems (VFS)</link> <filename>virt:/</filename> is not a virtual folder, "
"but a container for &URL;s from different file systems. It is used for &eg; "
"the <guilabel>Feed to Listbox</guilabel> feature of the search module and "
"the synchronizer. The location toolbar will display &eg; <filename>virt:/"
"Search results 1</filename> or <filename>virt:/Synchronise results 1</"
"filename>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>आभासी सञ्चिकातन्त्रम्</guilabel><link linkend=\"vfs\"> आभासी "
"सञ्चिकातन्त्राणि (VFS) २.</link><filename> virt:/ ९.</filename> आभासीपुटं न, अपितु "
"भिन्नसञ्चिकातन्त्रेभ्यः &amp;URL;s इत्यस्य पात्रम् । ⪚ इति कृते प्रयुक्तम्<guilabel> Listbox "
"मध्ये फीड् कुर्वन्तु</guilabel> अन्वेषणमॉड्यूलस्य तथा समन्वयकस्य विशेषता। स्थानसाधनपट्टिका ⪚ "
"प्रदर्शयिष्यति<filename> virt:/अन्वेषणपरिणामा 1</filename> वा<filename> virt:/"
"परिणामानां समन्वयनम् 1</filename> ."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Jump back</guilabel> or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> brings you back to your starting position when "
"you did create a new tab in the panel window. This feature is very handy if "
"you go deep into a folder tree, then you can return with one action to the "
"starting point. With <guilabel>Set jump back point here</guilabel> or "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> sets "
"the current folder as a jump back point."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>पृष्ठतः कूदन्तु</guilabel> अथवा <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> भवन्तं पुनः भवतः आरम्भस्थानं प्रति आनयति यदा भवन्तः "
"फलकविण्डो मध्ये नूतनं ट्याब् निर्मितवन्तः । यदि भवान् समुच्चय वृक्षे गभीरं गच्छति तर्हि एतत् "
"विशेषता अतीव सुलभं भवति, ततः एकेन क्रियायाः सह आरम्भबिन्दुं प्रति प्रत्यागन्तुं शक्नोति । "
"<guilabel>अत्र कूर्दनं पृष्ठबिन्दुं सेट् कुर्वन्तु</guilabel> अथवा <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> वर्तमानपुटं जम्प बैक् बिन्दुरूपेण सेट् "
"करोति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Manage bookmarks</title>"
msgstr "<title>बुकमार्कं प्रबन्धयन्तु</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit and organize your bookmarks, by clicking the <guibutton>BookMan II</"
"guibutton> button and selecting the <guimenuitem>Manage Bookmarks</"
"guimenuitem>, <application>KeditBookmarks</application> will be displayed. "
"This is where you can edit/remove and rearrange the bookmarks. "
"<application>KeditBookmarks</application> is a bookmark editor for "
"&konqueror;, &krusader; and other applications, which use the <ulink url="
"\"http://grail.sourceforge.net/info/xbel.html\">XBEL standard</ulink> for "
"the bookmark format. The bookmarks are stored in <filename> ~/.local/share/"
"krusader/krbookmarks.xml</filename>."
msgstr ""
"स्वस्य पुस्तकचिह्नानि सम्पादयितुं व्यवस्थितुं च <guibutton>BookMan II</guibutton> बटनं "
"नुत्वा <guimenuitem>पुस्तकचिह्नं प्रबन्धयन्तु</guimenuitem> इति चयनं कृत्वा "
"<application>KeditBookmarks</application> प्रदर्शितं भविष्यति अत्रैव भवान् "
"पुस्तकचिह्नानि सम्पादयितुं/निष्कासयितुं पुनः व्यवस्थितुं च शक्नोति । "
"<application>KeditBookmarks</application> इति &konqueror;, &krusader; तथा "
"अन्ये अनुप्रयोगाः, ये पुस्तकचिह्नस्वरूपस्य कृते <ulink url=\"http://grail.sourceforge.net/"
"info/xbel.html\">XBEL मानक</ulink> इत्यस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्ति । पुस्तकचिह्नानि "
"<filename> ~/.local/share/krusader/krbookmarks.xml</filename> इत्यत्र संगृहीताः "
"सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default folder for the bookmarks file <filename>krusader/krbookmarks."
"xml</filename> is <filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/share</filename>. "
"You can determine the needed folder in your system using the "
"<userinput>qtpaths --paths GenericDataLocation</userinput> command in "
"terminal."
msgstr ""
"<filename>krusader/krbookmarks.xml</filename> इति पुस्तकचिह्नसञ्चिकायाः "
"पूर्वनिर्धारितं पुटं <filename class=\"directory\">~/.local/share</filename> अस्ति "
"। टर्मिनल् मध्ये <userinput>qtpaths --paths GenericDataLocation</userinput> "
"आदेशस्य उपयोगेन भवान् स्वप्रणाल्यां आवश्यकं पुटं निर्धारयितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This local file exists only if you have edited &krusader; bookmarks. It will "
"be created after the first run of <application>KeditBookmarks</application> "
"from &krusader;."
msgstr ""
"इयं स्थानीयसञ्चिका केवलं तदा एव विद्यते यदा भवान् &krusader; पुस्तकचिह्नानि। &krusader;"
"तः <application>KeditBookmarks</application> इत्यस्य प्रथमस्य चालनस्य अनन्तरं "
"निर्मितं भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default system bookmarks are stored in the <filename>kfileplaces/"
"bookmarks.xml</filename> file in the folder which can be determined using "
"the <userinput>qtpaths --paths GenericDataLocation</userinput> command."
msgstr ""
"पूर्वनिर्धारितप्रणालीपुस्तकचिह्नानि पुटे <filename>kfileplaces/bookmarks.xml</"
"filename> सञ्चिकायां संगृह्यन्ते यत् <userinput>qtpaths --paths GenericDataLocation</"
"userinput> आदेशस्य उपयोगेन निर्धारयितुं शक्यते"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<application>KeditBookmarks</application> is easy to use, however, if you "
"need more information, please read the <ulink url=\"help:/keditbookmarks/"
"index.html\">KeditBookmarks handbook</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<application>KeditBookmarks</application> इत्यस्य उपयोगः सुलभः अस्ति तथापि यदि "
"भवतः अधिकसूचना आवश्यकी अस्ति तर्हि कृपया <ulink url=\"help:/keditbookmarks/index."
"html\">KeditBookmarks handbook</ulink> पठन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<title><application>KeditBookmarks</application> Bookmark Manager</title>"
msgstr ""
"<title>&lt;application&gt;KeditBookmarks&lt;/application&gt; "
"पुस्तकचिह्नप्रबन्धकः</title>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: bookmarks.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase><application>KeditBookmarks</application> Bookmark Manager</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase><application>KeditBookmarks</application> पुस्तकचिह्नप्रबन्धकः</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: bookmarks.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks as action buttons on the Toolbar"
msgstr "Toolbar इत्यत्र action buttons इति बुकमार्कं करोति"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bookmarks can be placed as buttons on the <link linkend=\"mainwindow\">Main "
"Toolbar</link> or the <link linkend=\"actions_toolbar\">Actions Toolbar</"
"link>. You can even make a key-binding for them:"
msgstr ""
"पुस्तकचिह्नानि बटनरूपेण स्थापयितुं शक्यन्ते<link linkend=\"mainwindow\"> मुख्य साधनपट्टी</"
"link> इति वा<link linkend=\"actions_toolbar\"> क्रियाः साधनपट्टिका</link> . "
"तेषां कृते कील-बन्धनम् अपि कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति:"

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create your <link linkend=\"bookman\">Bookmarks</link>."
msgstr "भवतः सृजतु<link linkend=\"bookman\"> बुकमार्क्स</link> ."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want, create keybindings for the bookmarks in the <link linkend="
"\"key_bindings\">Configure Shortcuts</link> window "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Shortcuts..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"यदि इच्छति तर्हि मध्ये पुस्तकचिह्नानां कृते कीबाइंडिङ्ग्स् रचयन्तु<link linkend="
"\"key_bindings\"> शॉर्टकट् विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु</link> कोष्ठ (<menuchoice><guimenu> "
"सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem> शॉर्टकट् विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> )."

#. Tag: para
#: bookmarks.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add your bookmarks as action buttons on the <link linkend=\"mainwindow"
"\">Main Toolbar</link> or the <link linkend=\"actions_toolbar\">Actions "
"Toolbar</link> with the <guilabel>Configure Toolbars...</guilabel> window "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure Toolbars...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>)."
msgstr ""
"इत्यस्य उपरि क्रियाबटनरूपेण स्वस्य पुस्तकचिह्नानि योजयन्तु<link linkend=\"mainwindow\"> "
"मुख्य साधनपट्टी</link> इति वा<link linkend=\"actions_toolbar\"> क्रियाः "
"साधनपट्टिका</link> सह<guilabel> टूलबार विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु...</guilabel> कोष्ठ "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu> सेटिंग्स्</guimenu><guimenuitem> टूलबार विन्यस्तं कुर्वन्तु...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> )."
